---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About - Your Name" description="Startup founder, product builder, and relentless optimist. Learn more about my journey and what drives me.">
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-image">
          <div class="image-wrapper">
            <div class="image-placeholder">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
                <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
              </svg>
              <span>Your Photo</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-intro">
          <span class="badge">About Me</span>
          <h1>I turn ideas into <span class="text-gradient">products</span></h1>
          <p class="lead">
            I'm a startup founder and product builder with a passion for creating things that 
            matter. Over the past 8+ years, I've founded multiple companies, built products 
            used by thousands, and learned more from failures than successes.
          </p>
          <p>
            Currently, I'm focused on [your current venture or focus area]. Previously, I 
            [your previous experience]. I believe the best products come from understanding 
            people deeply and shipping relentlessly.
          </p>
          <div class="about-links">
            <a href="https://twitter.com/yourhandle" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-pill">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M22 4s-.7 2.1-2 3.4c1.6 10-9.4 17.3-18 11.6 2.2.1 4.4-.6 6-2C3 15.5.5 9.6 3 5c2.2 2.6 5.6 4.1 9 4-.9-4.2 4-6.6 7-3.8 1.1 0 3-1.2 3-1.2z"></path>
              </svg>
              Twitter
            </a>
            <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/yourhandle" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-pill">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"></path>
                <rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="12"></rect>
                <circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"></circle>
              </svg>
              LinkedIn
            </a>
            <a href="https://github.com/yourhandle" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-pill">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M9 19c-5 1.5-5-2.5-7-3m14 6v-3.87a3.37 3.37 0 0 0-.94-2.61c3.14-.35 6.44-1.54 6.44-7A5.44 5.44 0 0 0 20 4.77 5.07 5.07 0 0 0 19.91 1S18.73.65 16 2.48a13.38 13.38 0 0 0-7 0C6.27.65 5.09 1 5.09 1A5.07 5.07 0 0 0 5 4.77a5.44 5.44 0 0 0-1.5 3.78c0 5.42 3.3 6.61 6.44 7A3.37 3.37 0 0 0 9 18.13V22"></path>
              </svg>
              GitHub
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="journey-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="badge">Journey</span>
        <h2>How I Got Here</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <span class="timeline-date">2024 - Present</span>
            <h3>Current Venture</h3>
            <p>Building something new in stealth mode. Focused on solving [problem] for [audience].</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <span class="timeline-date">2021 - 2024</span>
            <h3>Second Company</h3>
            <p>Founded and scaled a B2B SaaS company to $X ARR. Led product and engineering teams. Exited in 2024.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <span class="timeline-date">2018 - 2021</span>
            <h3>First Startup</h3>
            <p>Built my first product from scratch. Made every mistake in the book. Learned more than any degree could teach.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <span class="timeline-date">2015 - 2018</span>
            <h3>The Beginning</h3>
            <p>Started as a developer, quickly realized I wanted to build entire products, not just features.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="values-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="badge">Philosophy</span>
        <h2>What I Believe</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Ship Fast, Learn Faster</h3>
          <p>Perfect is the enemy of good. Get it out there, learn from real users, iterate relentlessly.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
              <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path>
              <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Users First, Always</h3>
          <p>The best products come from deep empathy. Talk to users every day. Solve real problems.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
              <path d="M12 6v6l4 2"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Long-Term Thinking</h3>
          <p>Build for the future, not just the next quarter. Sustainable growth beats vanity metrics.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M4 19.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 17H20"></path>
              <path d="M6.5 2H20v20H6.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Never Stop Learning</h3>
          <p>The moment you think you know everything is the moment you start falling behind.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact-section" id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="contact-card">
        <div class="contact-content">
          <span class="badge">Get in Touch</span>
          <h2>Let's Talk</h2>
          <p>
            Whether you're working on something interesting, looking for advice, or just want 
            to say hi â€” I'd love to hear from you. I try to respond to everyone.
          </p>
          
          <div class="contact-methods">
            <a href="mailto:hello@yourname.com" class="contact-method">
              <div class="method-icon">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"></path>
                  <polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"></polyline>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="method-label">Email</span>
                <span class="method-value">hello@yourname.com</span>
              </div>
            </a>
            
            <a href="https://twitter.com/yourhandle" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-method">
              <div class="method-icon">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <path d="M22 4s-.7 2.1-2 3.4c1.6 10-9.4 17.3-18 11.6 2.2.1 4.4-.6 6-2C3 15.5.5 9.6 3 5c2.2 2.6 5.6 4.1 9 4-.9-4.2 4-6.6 7-3.8 1.1 0 3-1.2 3-1.2z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="method-label">Twitter/X</span>
                <span class="method-value">@yourhandle</span>
              </div>
            </a>
            
            <a href="https://cal.com/yourhandle" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-method">
              <div class="method-icon">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
                  <line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"></line>
                  <line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"></line>
                  <line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"></line>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="method-label">Schedule a Call</span>
                <span class="method-value">Book 30 min</span>
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
  }
  
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 320px 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-3xl);
    align-items: start;
  }
  
  .about-image {
    position: sticky;
    top: calc(var(--nav-height) + var(--space-xl));
  }
  
  .image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  
  .image-placeholder {
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    background: var(--gradient-subtle);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }
  
  .image-placeholder span {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  
  
  .badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-md);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    background: var(--color-accent-light);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  
  .about-intro h1 {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }
  
  .about-intro .lead {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }
  
  .about-intro p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  
  .about-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }
  
  .social-pill {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all var(--transition-fast);
  }
  
  .social-pill:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    background: var(--color-accent-light);
  }
  
  /* Journey Section */
  .journey-section {
    padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  }
  
  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
  }
  
  .section-header h2 {
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
  }
  
  .timeline {
    max-width: 40rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: var(--color-border);
  }
  
  .timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: var(--space-2xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }
  
  .timeline-item:last-child {
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }
  
  .timeline-marker {
    position: absolute;
    left: -5px;
    top: 4px;
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 3px solid var(--color-bg-secondary);
  }
  
  .timeline-date {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    display: block;
  }
  
  .timeline-content h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
  
  .timeline-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  /* Values Section */
  .values-section {
    padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
  }
  
  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }
  
  .value-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  
  .value-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 3rem;
    height: 3rem;
    background: var(--color-accent-light);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }
  
  .value-card h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
  
  .value-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  /* Contact Section */
  .contact-section {
    padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  }
  
  .contact-card {
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: var(--space-3xl);
  }
  
  .contact-content {
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .contact-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  
  .contact-content > p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    max-width: 32rem;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-2xl);
  }
  
  .contact-methods {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }
  
  .contact-method {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all var(--transition-fast);
    text-align: left;
  }
  
  .contact-method:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  
  .method-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 2.5rem;
    height: 2.5rem;
    background: var(--color-accent-light);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  
  .method-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }
  
  .method-value {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  
  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-xl);
    }
    
    .about-image {
      position: static;
      max-width: 240px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .about-intro {
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .about-links {
      justify-content: center;
    }
    
    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .contact-methods {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .contact-card {
      padding: var(--space-xl);
    }
  }
</style>
